  m_Name: 2_AllPotions
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPCDialogue
  dialogueLines:
  - You've learned the old recipes well.
  - But knowing a recipe is not enough.
  - To create the Moonheart Elixir, the brews themselves must be prepared.
  - Each potion carries a different aspect of restoration.
  - Only when all four are complete can the final elixir be created.
  - Take your time, dear.
  - Moonwardens were never meant to rush their work.
  - The final elixir requires all four restorative brews.
  - Each one strengthens the magical world in a different way.
  - Wonderful...
  - You've gathered every piece needed for the final restoration.
